CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 12, 1957, pg. A15 reads: "Sara Lou Harris...and friends..in a fashion show sponsored by the Pittsburgh National Council of Negro Women, Saturday night."
